reviews:
Pros:
looks a very decent size in the bag;
heart is nice and crispy with a mild flavour, really enjoyable as the basis for a salad.

Cons:
lettuce was bunged (yes, bunged) in the bag, at least 12 outer leaves (it is big!) folded/bruised/crushed/torn;
because of the way it was 'packed' half of the lettuce was discarded;
a litle dirt but not unsurmountable;
not really as appetising as the photo suggessted;
nothing on the bag labelling to suggest that the lettuce is, in fact, biodynamic.
